## ğŸ› ï¸ Development

This project uses Poetry for dependency management. To set up the development environment:

```bash
# Install Poetry
curl -sSL https://install.python-poetry.org | python3 -

# Install dependencies
poetry install

# Run the CLI
poetry run clicerin
```

